These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, mirinda, cola, milk, iced-tea, lemonade
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, malaysian, mexican, thai, italian, canadian, colombian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, rugby, rowing, badminton, cycling, parkour
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, tram, taxi, roller, trike, airplane
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is the thai##1
 3. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the malaysian is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the russian is on the right of the colombian##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the italian##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the airplane and the canadian##2
 9. the italian is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the person drinking milk##1
12. the person drinking milk is the person driving the bus##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the mexican##1
14. the canadian is the person driving the tram##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the left of the colombian##1
16. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
17. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the mexican##1
18. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the italian##1
19. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | iced-tea        | milk | mirinda      | cola     | hot-chocolate      | lemonade     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | thai         | colombian   | russian | canadian    | italian | mexican |
| Sport         | rugby | badminton | handball | lacrosse | parkour  | cycling  | rowing    |
