11. the fan of soul is the person eating pepper##1
12. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
13. the fan of gospel is between the person eating pear and the fan of salsa##2
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
16. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
17. the person eating busrot is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
18. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating banana##1
